title: Fendi Mini Selleria Baguette 2Way Bag
description: Fendi mini Selleria Baguette 2way bag in navy blue grainy calfskin leather. Featuring silver-toned hardware, tone-to-tone maxi stitching, detachable leather top handle & FF square logo on front flap. The magnetic button closure opens to a navy blue smooth leather interior with a card slot. Approx. dimensions: 19cm(L) x 12cm(H) x 5cm(D), handle drop 8cm, detachable chain with leather pad strap drop: 41cm. Accompanied by a Fendi dustbag and tag card.
